  <div><h3>How to get started with this hobby?</h3></div>
  <p>This hobby can definitely be fun but it requires a LOT of work. For you to play the game, you have to build and paint models so that it is more immersive on the table top. 
    This isn't a video game where you are playing to win. You are playing for the experience. With that being said, starting out small is definitely the right move when starting a new hobby.
  </p>

  <p>On a barebones level, you should have the following to start working with miniature modeling:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Some <a class="links" href="https://www.games-workshop.com/en-US/Start-Collecting-Vanguard-Space-Marines-2019/" target="_blank">models</a> for an army that you enjoy the look of</li>
    <li>Simple cutting tools such as <a class="links" href="https://www.amazon.com/Xuron-2175ET-Professional-Sprue-Cutter/dp/B001TMZ7QA/" target="_blank">modeling cutters</a> and a <a class="links" href="https://www.amazon.com/Tamiya-74098-Modeler-Knife-Pro/dp/B0042VKAP8/" target="_blank">modeling knife</a></li>
    <li><a class="links" href="https://www.games-workshop.com/en-US/Citadel-Plastic-Glue-2016-Global/" target="_blank">Plastic</a> or super glue to glue the model together</li>
    <li>A <a class="links" href="https://www.games-workshop.com/en-US/Spray-Chaos-Black-Global-2019/" target="_blank">spray primer</a> to prime your models for painting</li>
    <li>A couple different <a class="links" href="https://www.amazon.com/Tamiya-America-Modeling-Standard-TAM87067/dp/B000J49XD2/" target="_blank">paint brushes</a> and a small selection of <a class="links" href="https://www.amazon.com/Vallejo-Basic-Colors-Paint-17ml/dp/B009162PWU/ref=sr_1_6?crid=WTJ1U7I3VFXI&dchild=1&keywords=model+paints+for+plastic+models+vallejo&qid=1599937869&sprefix=Model+Paints+for+Plastic+Models+va%2Caps%2C174&sr=8-6/" target="_blank">model paints</a> to use</li>
    <li>A mixing plate (such as a ceramic tile) and a glass of water</li>
    <li>Some <a class="links" href="https://www.games-workshop.com/en-US/Middenland-Tufts/" target="_blank">basing material</a> and <a class="links" href="https://www.games-workshop.com/en-US/Technical-Agrellan-Earth-2019/" target="_blank">texture paint</a> add the finishing touches to the model's base</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Once you have all of that, you can then begin your modeling adventure! Once you start, you'll become quite addicted to building your models and army!</p>
